edu.cnm.deepdive.project_titan.service

Interface BaseFluentAsyncTask.ProgressListener<Progress>

  • Type Parameters:
    Progress - type of individual values provided by the asynchronous task for progress updates (consumed by BaseFluentAsyncTask.onProgressUpdate(Object[])), or (usually) Void if no progress updates will be made.
    Enclosing class:
    BaseFluentAsyncTask<Params,Progress,Intermediate,Result>

    public static interface BaseFluentAsyncTask.ProgressListener<Progress>
    Declares an update(Object[]) method that can be implemented to provide UI updates (for example) while a background task is ongoing.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void update(Progress... values)
      Performs progress updates on the UI, or other progress updates that originate on the UI thread, and are thus asynchronous with background processing.
